missionDescription: 1 Star missions require a rider with a combat level >1000 to perform.
2 Star missions require a rider with a combat level >5000 to perform.
3 Star missions require a rider with a combat level >9000 to perform.
4 Star missions require a rider with a combat level >13000 to perform.
5 Star missions require a rider with a combat level >17000 to perform.
